{"tid":390390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局副局長蔡若蓮兒子墮樓身亡","createTime":"2017-09-07T05:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:29:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76db1d0976f75282d39c135accef7629c385e57b","tid":390390,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170907%2Fbkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html&d=sO0Px8KvEZm8glN2KaOhaS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=66caa55b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html</a><br />\n尖沙咀柯士甸道擎天半島發生墮樓案，早上11時許，大廈保安員突聞巨響，發現一名20餘歲男子倒臥在第3座平台對開，一臉鮮血陷入昏迷，於是報警。救護員及消防員到場，為傷者急救後送院，惜告死亡。警方初步相信男子由40多層高墮下，正調查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，墮樓男子為教育局副局長蔡若蓮的兒子，蔡之前曾任教聯會副主席。"},{"pid":"a0d47941023c516f5f8e012a76e9978b51cb6f21","tid":390390,"uid":62693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c7ff9c1b8f079758f97582eac2c85f9f31485c","tid":390390,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"588291f0f4e02ae2b6c6eb899c7dfffea2f55586","tid":390390,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c6ed1d57e188bd65210362d0d3f2b63fed8c185","tid":390390,"